UBS - Wikipedia






















 







UBS

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For other uses, see UBS (disambiguation).

UBS Group AG





Type

Aktiengesellschaft (AG)
Public company


Traded as
SIX: UBSG SIX: UBSN
NYSE: UBS


Industry
Banking, Financial services


